-- ALTER VIEW kpivis.dim_parcela_calculo_kpi
-- AS
SELECT
[CICLO_TERRITORIO]
,[VP]
,[VR]
,[VRE]
,[TOTAL_TFT]
,[DIAS_UTEIS]
,[VISITAS_ABATER]
,[OBJETIVO_VISITA_DIA]
,[DIAS_VISITACAO]
,[VR_CLM]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/KPI Visitacao/dimensao_parcela_calculo_kpi.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
[CICLO_TERRITORIO]		VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VP]					VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VR]					VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VRE]					VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[TOTAL_TFT]			VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIAS_UTEIS]			VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VISITAS_ABATER]		VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[OBJETIVO_VISITA_DIA]	VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[DIAS_VISITACAO]		VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[VR_CLM]				VARCHAR(20) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8

    ) as ROW
